{"tid":1170212,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貿戰演變民族戰？中國消費者自發封殺Apple　轉買華為","createTime":"2019-05-25T00:57:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T06:57:23.000Z","uid":22675,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"be13865b2a994e57cbb2802f51620efa0879f30c","tid":1170212,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T00:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20190522/photo/bkn-20190522154521887-0522_00842_001_01p.jpg?20190522200351\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20190522%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190522154521887-0522_00842_001_01p.jpg%3F20190522200351&h=20c54881&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n外國傳媒報道，中美貿易戰似乎提升至「民族主義」層面。在美國封殺華為後，中國消費者正紛紛表態支持華為產品，抵制蘋果公司(Apple Inc.)。<br />\n<br />\n報道綜合多家媒體消息，中國消費者已紛紛轉軚支持國產華為，認為中國科技日漸發達，消費市場龐大，不見得華為需要倚賴美國供應鏈。同時，中國消費者對於華為給予正面支持，以實際行動買華為產品，並開始抵制Apple。 <br />\n<br />\n目前中國市場佔蘋果公司整體銷售約17%。華為則是全球市佔第2大手機廠商，僅次於三星。"},{"pid":"4436a15933f4975b4b4ca5d51b5ab11db364c113","tid":1170212,"uid":24570,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T00:58:33.000Z","msg":"支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ae5e9abda1f284aba11825b51be2f398ea78538","tid":1170212,"uid":18587,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:19:16.000Z","msg":"17%係計係中國apple買既機？咁一車車黎香港買機既計唔計？"},{"pid":"3c03721776994bad9f295016e9da7f06f14190bb","tid":1170212,"uid":60563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T01:33:34.000Z","msg":"用iPhone發文被笑 向太︰應該先買華為才發微博<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1166007\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1166007</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你地既愛國心連千幾蚊都唔值呀"},{"pid":"fdebd2c5adf4d61f4254d46e81c6a5225b35fac4","tid":1170212,"uid":66381,"like":1,"dislike":0